{
  "text": "1) K-spectrum based method such as Quake (2010), Lighter (2014) [CITATION_1] , Reptile (2010) [CITATION_2] , BLESS (2014) [CITATION_3] hammer (2011), Musket (2013), HECTOR (2014) and RACER (2013). These tools correct the errors on k-mer incidence.",
